data.description: Enjoy a unique one-of-a-kind Tangerine Community home. The interior of this custom home was designed personally by the owner, making it different from any other homes in the community. The community is located close to restaurants & entertainment. Privately situated on its own lot, this 3-bedroom, 3.5 bath, with a den/office or possible 4th bedroom, 2819 sq. ft. home boasts a beautifully landscaped, wrap-around yard w/ ample outdoor living space & an awesome pool/spa. The home features a modern & luxurious design, beautifully stained wood & glass entry door that leads into a formal entry, soaring 10' ceilings & an open floor plan. The great room features a gas fireplace, beautiful tile flooring. The gourmet kitchen boasts high-end stainless-steel appliances; 5-burner gas stove, oven, warming drawer and wine refrigerator, tons of storage & a kitchen island that opens to the great room. The 2nd level boasts two large master suites. The first master features stunning panoramic views, fireplace, patio, beautiful bath w/ dual vanities & an oversized shower w/ multiple shower heads & walk-in closet. The second bedroom equally stunning w/  mountain views. The casita w/ private entry, balcony, fully functioning kitchen. Other features include, Nest controlled HVAC, custom lighting & sound system (all voice controlled), water filtration/softening system,tankless water heater & much more! FEE-Simple land (you own the land). Owned 28 panel Solar system!!!
